TI  - Fishing to live or living to fish: Job satisfaction and identity of west coast fishermen
T2  - AMBIO
KW  - Factor analysis
KW  - Fisheries
KW  - Identity
KW  - Job satisfaction
KW  - Social capital
KW  - Well being
KW  - MANAGEMENT
