TI  - Burnout in nurses - the relationship between social capital in hospitals and emotional exhaustion
T2  - JOURNAL OF CLINICAL NURSING
KW  - burnout
KW  - emotional exhaustion
KW  - nurses
KW  - nursing
KW  - social capital
KW  - workload
KW  - JOB-SATISFACTION
KW  - HEALTH OUTCOMES
KW  - MISSING-DATA
