TI  - The secrets to successful entrepreneurship: how occupational experience shapes the creation and performance of start-ups
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ENTREPRENEURIAL BEHAVIOR & RESEARCH
KW  - Occupational experience
KW  - Entrepreneurial entry
KW  - Entrepreneurial performance
KW  - EARLY INTERNATIONALIZATION
KW  - PERSONALITY-TRAITS
