TI  - Centrality and Charisma: Comparing How Leader Networks <i>and</i> Attributions Affect Team Performance
T2  - JOURNAL OF APPLIED PSYCHOLOGY
KW  - social networks
KW  - leader
KW  - centrality
KW  - charisma
KW  - team performance
KW  - TRANSFORMATIONAL LEADERSHIP
KW  - SOCIAL NETWORKS
KW  - ORGANIZATIONAL PERFORMANCE
KW  - ENVIRONMENTAL UNCERTAINTY
