TI  - Feeling like a million miles away from home? Well-being at work of expatriates in the resources sector in Indonesia
T2  - GERMAN JOURNAL OF HUMAN RESOURCE MANAGEMENT-ZEITSCHRIFT FUR PERSONALFORSCHUNG
KW  - Expatriates
