TI  - HOW ORGANIZATIONAL EMBEDDEDNESS AND AFFECTIVE COMMITMENT INFLUENCE JOB CRAFTING
T2  - SOCIAL BEHAVIOR AND PERSONALITY
KW  - job crafting
KW  - organizational embeddedness
