TI  - Social Class and Changes in Australian Women's Affect and Alcohol Consumption During COVID-19
T2  - FRONTIERS IN PUBLIC HEALTH
KW  - alcohol
KW  - women
KW  - social class
KW  - survey
KW  - pandemic (COVID-19)
KW  - anxiety
