TI  - "We Won't Retire Without Skeletons in the Closet": Healthcare-Related Regrets Among Physicians and Nurses in German-Speaking Swiss Hospitals
T2  - QUALITATIVE HEALTH RESEARCH
KW  - healthcare-related regret
KW  - healthcare professionals
KW  - Switzerland
