TI  - Can I Work With Older Workers if I Hold Stereotypes Regarding Their Competence? The Consequences for Stereotype Holders
T2  - CANADIAN JOURNAL OF BEHAVIOURAL SCIENCE-REVUE CANADIENNE DES SCIENCES DU COMPORTEMENT
KW  - age stereotypes
KW  - age-diverse workforce
