TI  - Born in a tour guide's family: how can tourism employment fuel intergenerational social mobility?
T2  - CURRENT ISSUES IN TOURISM
KW  - Intergenerational social mobility
KW  - tourism labour
KW  - tourism employment
KW  - tour guide
KW  - capital
KW  - sustainable tourism development
