TI  - RETRACTED: Why Connect? Moral Consequences of Networking With a Promotion or Prevention Focus (Retracted article. See vol. 125, pg. 648, 2023)
T2  - JOURNAL OF PERSONALITY AND SOCIAL PSYCHOLOGY
KW  - networking
