TI  - Feel the Pressure? Normative Pressures as a Unifying Mechanism for Relational Antecedents of Employee Turnover
T2  - HUMAN RESOURCE MANAGEMENT
KW  - LEADER-MEMBER EXCHANGE
KW  - PERCEIVED ORGANIZATIONAL SUPPORT
KW  - PROXIMAL WITHDRAWAL STATES
KW  - THE-JOB EMBEDDEDNESS
