TI  - Educational consequences of mental disorders treated in hospital.: A 31-year follow-up of the Northern Finland 1966 Birth Cohort
T2  - PSYCHOLOGICAL MEDICINE
KW  - ACADEMIC-ACHIEVEMENT
KW  - SCHOOL PERFORMANCE
KW  - SEX-DIFFERENCES
KW  - SOCIAL-CLASS
