TI  - An Assessment of the "Capital" Indicators for Measuring Socioeconomic Status of High School Students and the Influence on Family and School Stressors
T2  - CHILD INDICATORS RESEARCH
KW  - Socioeconomic indicator
KW  - Youths
KW  - Stress
KW  - Social capital
KW  - Material capital
KW  - Human capital
