TI  - Vital Linkages: A Study of the Role of Linking Social Capital in a Philippine Disaster Recovery and Rebuilding Effort
T2  - SOCIAL JUSTICE RESEARCH
KW  - Disaster recovery
KW  - Political transformation
KW  - Social justice
KW  - Community development
KW  - Social capital
KW  - Linking capital
KW  - STATE
KW  - MANAGEMENT
KW  - GOVERNMENT
