TI  - Researching health-related quality of life at a community level: results from a population survey conducted in Burgas, Bulgaria
T2  - HEALTH PROMOTION INTERNATIONAL
KW  - community health promotion
KW  - determinants of health
KW  - Eastern Europe
KW  - quality of life
KW  - SELF-REPORTED HEALTH
KW  - DIVIDE
KW  - QUESTIONNAIRE
KW  - EUROPE
KW  - UNION
