TI  - Diverging death risks: Mortality as a corollary of economic, social, cultural and person capital
T2  - SSM-POPULATION HEALTH
KW  - Mortality
KW  - Socioeconomic factors
KW  - Social determinants of health
KW  - Capital
KW  - HEALTH INEQUALITIES
KW  - SOCIOECONOMIC-STATUS
KW  - ATTRACTIVENESS
KW  - DETERMINANTS
