TI  - A framework for identifying and mitigating the equity harms of COVID-19 policy interventions
T2  - JOURNAL OF CLINICAL EPIDEMIOLOGY
KW  - COVID-19
KW  - Equity
KW  - Inequity
KW  - Adverse effects
KW  - Public health
